  • java.lang.Object

    LeicaGSIFileTools

    private class LeicaGSIFileTools.GSIBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines an inner object for better access to elements and so on.

    In the first version this GSIBlock object is used only internally in this class. Maybe later on, there will be a good reason to make an own public class from it.
